description:
&lt;p&gt;The Wyre Forest Health Partnership which was formed three years ago and now consists of six surgeries based in the beautiful Wyre Forest area. We have 44 GPs and over 200 staff looking after over 73,000 patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking to recruit a Junior Admin Assistant for our Church Street Surgery. The hours of work are 37 hours per week - Monday to Friday between the hours of 8.00 am - 6.30 pm.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To be responsible for undertaking a wide range of reception and administrative duties which includes providing full administration support to the Reception team and project a positive and friendly image to patients and other visitors, either in person or via the telephone.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Wyre Forest Health Partnership are passionate about providing our patients with a first class service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a person who is:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Educated to a good level of education in Mathematics and English language.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience of working in a customer focussed role would be advantageous.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have excellent communication skills and able to learn computer software packages.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To apply for this post, please apply on NHS Jobs.&lt;/p&gt;
